title: Do You Know What You Want?
itunes:title: Do You Know What You Want?
description:
Episode 506 - After coaching thousands of people, I have found that one of the main reasons that people do not succeed is because they don't know what they want. They have an idea but are not 100% clear on what it is. You have to realize, you will never hit a target that you cannot see. So, in this episode I will teach you how to get clear on your goals!
